org.tensorics.core.math.predicates

Interface BinaryPredicate<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the operands
    All Superinterfaces:
    BinaryFunction<T,java.lang.Boolean>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractQuantityStatisticPredicate, IsEqualTo, IsNotEqualTo, QuantityGreaterPredicate, QuantityLessPredicate

    public interface BinaryPredicate<T>
extends BinaryFunction<T,java.lang.Boolean>
    Represents a predicate (boolean-valued function) of two arguments of the same type. This is a functional interface whose functional method is test(Object, Object).

    • Method Summary
